  <abstract>&lt;DIV STYLE="text-align:Left;">&lt;DIV>&lt;DIV>&lt;P STYLE="margin:0 0 11 0;">&lt;SPAN STYLE="font-size:12pt">This dataset provides historical coal mine maps and locations.
